<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="si">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EduAI Scanner</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f9; text-align: center; padding: 50px; }
        .container { background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: inline-block; }
        h1 { color: #2c3e50; }
        .upload-btn { background: #3498db; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>📚 EduAI Scanner</h1>
        <p>ඔබේ ලේඛන හෝ පින්තූර මෙතැනින් ස්කෑන් කරන්න.</p>
        <input type="file" id="fileInput" hidden>
        <button class="upload-btn" onclick="document.getElementById('fileInput').click()">ගොනුව තෝරන්න</button>
        <div id="result" style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold; color: #27ae60;"></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
